snippet.title: Amber Heard Brags About Securing Role In 2 More Aquaman Movies!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Signing A New Deal For 2 More Aquaman Movies And Brags About It.

✅ SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiKzneRB4I4eTN_bHEqV-gg?sub_confirmation=1

It has been confirmed that Amber Heard isn’t being left out of Aquaman 2, but apparently, she may have been signed for further Aquaman films as well! With millions of fans already campaigning for Heard not to appear on Aquaman 2, after her feud with ex-partner Johnny Depp, the news of her supposedly being signed for further Aquaman films, as well as in other franchises certainly won’t satisfy them one bit. 

#AmberHeard #Aquaman2
